<p>REFUTE</p>
<p>refutare refers to a refutation by any means and the word refers specifically to a defensive act of refutation of arguments directed against him.</p>
<p>confutare refers to an offensive act of refutation in exposing the nullity of an opponent's arguments.</p></note></bibl>
